{
  "page": "Cleyton Caswell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the supporter of Stannis Baratheon, see <a href=\"/index.php/Clayton_Suggs\" title=\"Clayton Suggs\">Clayton Suggs</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\"><img alt=\"House Caswell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/50px-House_Caswell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/75px-House_Caswell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/100px-House_Caswell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Cleyton Caswell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\"><img alt=\"House Caswell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/50px-House_Caswell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/75px-House_Caswell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/100px-House_Caswell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Cleyton_Caswell_TSS_Comic.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cleyton Caswell TSS Comic.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/68/Cleyton_Caswell_TSS_Comic.jpg/300px-Cleyton_Caswell_TSS_Comic.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"/images/6/68/Cleyton_Caswell_TSS_Comic.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Cleyton Caswell by Mike S Miller for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">graphic novel</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\">House Caswell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafcleyton_caswell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafcleyton_caswell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Cleyton Caswell</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\">House Caswell</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cleyton_Caswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Near the start of the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys I Targaryen</a>, Cleyton was a handsome young man.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cleyton_Caswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Cleyton was a suitor of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>, a four-time widow. He attended her at <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a>, the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Webber\" title=\"House Webber\">House Webber</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cleyton_Caswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafcleyton_caswell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafcleyton_caswell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Cleyton Caswell.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403144734\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.124 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.456 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 589/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10529/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7127/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 782/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1707/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.290/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.82 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  438.902      1 -total\n 87.36%  383.438      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 86.92%  381.489      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.35%   49.803     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  8.14%   35.713      1 Template:For\n  5.13%   22.532      4 Template:Ref\n  4.49%   19.686      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.96%   17.384      4 Template:Ref/core\n  0.69%    3.016      1 Template:Refe